    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's ready for its next adventure! This car has been well-loved and is in really solid shape, making it a fantastic find for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs like a dream and is super comfortable for those longer trips. I've priced it to sell quickly, so come on by, grab the keys, and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 inline-six with high-pressure VANOS and individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and dampers. A driver-focused machine with a clean title, ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Mechanically sound. Title ready.",
      "price": 28500.0,
